The paper deals with natural language processing and machine comprehension, which are typically covered under the arXiv sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of neural networks and limited training data suggest that the paper could also be relevant to sub-categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the mention of word-embedding representations and the use of text suggest that the paper could also be relevant to sub-category cs.CV (Computer Vision), which often deals with image and text processing.
